Homework Class #13 Associations

1. Amazon 
	
	Users
		Fields
			UserID
			User Name
			User Address
			User Credit Card Info
		Associations
			Has Many transactions
			Has Many Reviews

	Transactions
		Fields
			Transaction ID
			Transaction amount
			Product Purchased
		Associations
			Belongs to Users
			Belongs to products

	Products
		Fields
			Product ID
			Cost
			Offering merchant
			Description
		Associations
			Belongs to Merchants
			Has Many Reviews
			Has Many transactions

	Merchants
		Fields
			Merchant ID
			Merchant Category
			Merchant Name
			Merchant address
		Associations
			Has Many Products

	Reviews
		Fields
			Review ID
			User ID
			Text
			Rating
		Associations
			Belongs to Products
			Belongs to Users


2. Linkedin

	Users
		Fields
			UserID
			User Name
			User Address
			User Credit Card Info
			Background description
		Associations
			Has Many Friends
			Has Many Subscriptions

	Friends
		Fields
			User ID
		Associations
			Belongs to Users

	Subscriptions
		Fields
			Transaction ID
			Transaction amount
			Type
			Subscription start date
			Subscription end date
		Associations
			Belongs to Users

